Shooter_nz wrote a review Oct 2019
Bangkok, Thailand141 contributions69 helpful votes
A great hotel to stay at when golfing in Danang, central to all courses and on the beach
Comfortable room, there was construction next door, but didn't hear a thing. Had breakfast on arrive, quick and easy, day two shot down to the deli/cafe downstairs, absolutely brilliant! Watching the pastry team making pastries and breads and was lucky enough to enjoy a sandwich fresh from the oven. The reception team were knowledgeable and very well organised.
Read more
Date of stay: August 2019
