Short but amazing!
What a great find! Amazing hotel right next to beach. Room very spacious, clean and comfortable, probably the best shower I have experienced anywhere! Fantastic rooftop bar/restaurant with stunning infinity pool. Breakfast buffet was huge with a wonderful selection. Staff, especially Vuong, extremely helpful - nothing to much trouble. Would stay here again.
